WEBVTT

00:06.507 --> 00:06.707
.

00:06.740 --> 00:07.641
male narrator:
IN THE CRIMINAL JUSTICE SYSTEM,

00:09.810 --> 00:12.246
SEXUALLY-BASED OFFENSES ARE
CONSIDERED ESPECIALLY HEINOUS.

00:12.280 --> 00:15.349
IN NEW YORK CITY, THE DEDICATED
DETECTIVES WHO INVESTIGATE

00:15.383 --> 00:17.818
THESE VICIOUS FELONIES ARE
MEMBERS OF AN ELITE SQUAD

00:17.851 --> 00:20.288
KNOWN AS
THE SPECIAL VICTIMS UNIT.

00:20.321 --> 00:22.456
THESE ARE THEIR STORIES.

00:31.499 --> 00:33.334
- WITH US TODAY,

00:33.367 --> 00:36.737
THE GREATEST
BASKETBALL PLAYER EVER.

00:36.770 --> 00:39.173
HE RETIRED THREE YEARS AGO,

00:39.207 --> 00:44.178
AND HIS LEGACY HAS ONLY GROWN
IN HIS ABSENCE.

00:44.212 --> 00:46.314
LADIES AND GENTLEMEN,

00:46.347 --> 00:49.217
THE ONE AND THE ONLY,

00:49.250 --> 00:51.685
SHAKIR "THE SHARK" WILKINS.

00:51.719 --> 00:54.355
[cheers and applause]

01:03.264 --> 01:04.798
- AS MY DAUGHTER MENTIONED,

01:04.832 --> 01:07.568
TODAY'S A VERY SPECIAL DAY
AT ORION BAY.

01:07.601 --> 01:10.538
TODAY WE ARE ANNOUNCING
THE WORST-KEPT SECRET

01:10.571 --> 01:12.173
IN THE GARMENT INDUSTRY:

01:12.206 --> 01:15.243
SHAKIR'S CONTRACT
HAS BEEN RENEWED.

01:15.276 --> 01:16.844
[cheers and applause]

01:16.877 --> 01:19.247
- HE'S NOT ONLY A GREAT WARRIOR,

01:19.280 --> 01:21.549
HE'S AN EVEN GREATER ROLE MODEL.

01:21.582 --> 01:24.852
AND HE WILL ALWAYS BE A PART
OF OUR ORION BAY FAMILY.

01:24.885 --> 01:26.354
[cheers and applause]

01:26.387 --> 01:27.421
- SHAKIR.

01:31.625 --> 01:33.894
- THANK YOU, MR. BAUER.

01:33.927 --> 01:37.665
IT'S AN HONOR, A PRIVILEGE,

01:37.698 --> 01:40.501
AND ONE HELL OF A PAYDAY.
[chuckles]

01:40.534 --> 01:42.370
- [female TV host]
WE'LL TAKE QUESTIONS NOW,

01:42.403 --> 01:43.904
WE'LL START WITH AL TRAUTWIG.

01:43.937 --> 01:45.339
- WHAT'S UP?
- HEY.

01:45.373 --> 01:47.175
SHAKIR LOOKS...

01:47.208 --> 01:48.876
GOOD.
- RIGHT.

01:48.909 --> 01:51.345
MOST OF THOSE GUYS GET A LITTLE
CHUBBY AFTER THEY RETIRE.

01:51.379 --> 01:53.181
- I SWEAR I DIDN'T HAVE
A GAMBLING PROBLEM

01:53.214 --> 01:54.515
TILL HE LEFT THE GAME.

01:54.548 --> 01:57.285
I NEVER LOST A DOLLAR
BETTING ON HIM.

01:59.220 --> 02:00.488
- THAT'S MY BOY.

02:00.521 --> 02:03.624
NICE JOB.
- THANK YOU, SIR.

02:03.657 --> 02:07.228
- WELL, I DON'T UNDERSTAND.
WHERE IS IT?

02:07.261 --> 02:10.164
- WHAT'S GOING ON, HONEY?
- SHAKIR'S DRIVER'S GONE AWOL.

02:10.198 --> 02:12.366
- WELL, UBER IT.

02:12.400 --> 02:13.334
CARLA CAN GO WITH.

02:13.367 --> 02:15.503
- UM, CAN'T SOMEONE ELSE
DO THAT?

02:15.536 --> 02:17.305
- IS THERE A PROBLEM?

02:17.338 --> 02:18.572
- SHAKIR.

02:18.606 --> 02:20.408
CARLA WILL GET YOU OUT OF HERE,
LET'S GO.

02:20.441 --> 02:22.243
HI, YES...

02:40.861 --> 02:43.264
- NO!
GET OFF OF ME!

02:43.297 --> 02:44.965
YOU CAN'T SHUT ME UP!

02:44.998 --> 02:47.901
I'M NOT YOUR THOT, YOU CAN'T
JUST MAKE THIS GO AWAY!

02:47.935 --> 02:50.271
HE KNOWS WHAT HE DID!
- CARLA, THAT'S ENOUGH!

02:50.304 --> 02:51.639
- YOUR LIFE JUST GETS
TO GO ON, HUH?

02:51.672 --> 02:53.441
MORE MONEY, MORE FAME,

02:53.474 --> 02:54.675
NO RESPONSIBILITY!
- GET HER OUT OF HERE,

02:54.708 --> 02:56.510
GET HER OUT OF HERE!
- GET OFF OF ME!

02:56.544 --> 02:58.279
- THE HELL IS SHE TALKING ABOUT?
- DAD, LET'S GO.

02:58.312 --> 02:59.747
LET'S GO, PLEASE.

02:59.780 --> 03:01.382
- YOU CAN'T SHUT ME UP!

03:01.415 --> 03:05.219
I'M NOT YOUR THOT--
- WHAT'S GOING ON?

03:05.253 --> 03:07.355
- UH, BREAKING NEWS
AT ORION BAY.

03:07.388 --> 03:08.789
YOU KNOW SHAKIR WILKINS?

03:08.822 --> 03:10.724
- UH, AMERICA'S HERO?
YEAH.

03:10.758 --> 03:13.227
- NOT ANYMORE.

03:13.261 --> 03:14.628
- GET YOUR HANDS OFF OF ME!

03:14.662 --> 03:16.830
HE'S NOT A ROLE MODEL,
HE'S A RAPIST!

03:16.864 --> 03:18.366
HE RAPED ME!

03:18.399 --> 03:19.667
- WHEN DID THIS HAPPEN?

03:19.700 --> 03:21.402
HALF HOUR AGO.
WANT ME TO TALK TO THIS GIRL?

03:21.435 --> 03:22.503
- WHERE ARE FIN AND ROLLINS?

03:22.536 --> 03:23.571
- AT A WORKING LUNCH.

03:23.604 --> 03:25.406
- GET 'EM BACK IN HERE.

03:31.512 --> 03:34.482
[dramatic music]

03:34.515 --> 03:42.523
*

03:45.793 --> 03:53.801
*

03:57.004 --> 04:05.279
*

04:19.026 --> 04:19.427
.

04:19.460 --> 04:20.060
- DO I HAVE TO TALK ABOUT THIS?

04:21.662 --> 04:22.996
- WELL, WE HAVE A VIDEO OF YOU
ATTACKING SHAKIR,

04:23.030 --> 04:25.899
SO IF HE PRESSES CHARGES,
THIS MIGHT HELP.

04:25.933 --> 04:28.636
- IF HE PRESSES CHARGES?
HE ASSAULTED ME.

04:28.669 --> 04:31.038
- IT DIDN'T LOOK THAT WAY
ON THE TAPE.

04:31.071 --> 04:33.807
- SHE'S NOT TALKING ABOUT TODAY.

04:33.841 --> 04:35.609
ARE YOU, CARLA?

04:35.643 --> 04:37.378
- NO.

04:38.779 --> 04:41.949
I'M TALKING ABOUT MEMORIAL DAY.

04:41.982 --> 04:43.050
- THREE MONTHS AGO?

04:44.852 --> 04:46.787
- CARLA, WHY DON'T YOU
HAVE A SEAT?

04:51.959 --> 04:55.696
- A SUMMER KICK-OFF
IN THE HAMPTONS.

04:55.729 --> 04:57.331
I DROVE SHAKIR BACK TO THE CITY

04:57.365 --> 04:59.833
AND HE INVITED ME TO HIS HOTEL
FOR A NIGHTCAP.

04:59.867 --> 05:03.537
- AT THE BAR,
OR DID YOU GO TO HIS ROOM?

05:03.571 --> 05:05.706
- THE LAST THING I REMEMBER...

05:05.739 --> 05:09.377
WAS HAVING A DRINK WITH HIM
AT THE HOTEL BAR.

05:09.410 --> 05:12.346
ONE DRINK.

05:12.380 --> 05:14.448
I WOKE UP IN HIS ROOM.

05:15.416 --> 05:17.117
IN HIS BED,
NAKED AND SORE.

05:17.150 --> 05:19.119
- DID YOU GO TO THE HOSPITAL
AFTERWARDS,

05:19.152 --> 05:22.956
OR CALL A DOCTOR?

05:22.990 --> 05:24.658
- NO.

05:24.692 --> 05:28.362
WHAT WAS I GONNA DO?
I DON'T REMEMBER ANYTHING.

05:28.396 --> 05:31.532
- WHAT MADE YOU DECIDE
TO CONFRONT HIM TODAY,

05:31.565 --> 05:33.066
AT A PRESS EVENT?

05:33.100 --> 05:34.635
- THERE WAS A PROBLEM
WITH HIS CAR,

05:34.668 --> 05:38.539
AND SO I WAS TOLD TO GET SHAKIR
BACK TO HIS HOTEL.

05:38.572 --> 05:40.574
IT TRIGGERED ME.

05:42.109 --> 05:43.677
LOOK, THIS IS A MISTAKE, OKAY?

05:43.711 --> 05:45.112
THERE'S NOTHING THAT YOU GUYS
CAN DO ABOUT IT,

05:45.145 --> 05:46.747
AND I'M PROBABLY GONNA LOSE
MY JOB AS IT IS--

05:46.780 --> 05:48.882
- HOLD ON, HOLD ON, ONE SEC.

05:48.916 --> 05:51.051
WHAT DO YOU MEAN BY THAT,
"LOSE YOUR JOB"?

05:51.084 --> 05:52.486
- ARE YOU SERIOUS?

05:52.520 --> 05:54.988
SHAKIR WILKINS IS
THE FACE OF ORION BAY.

05:55.022 --> 05:57.925
IT'S LIKE PEEING
ON MOUNT RUSHMORE.

05:57.958 --> 05:59.560
I MEAN, MR. BAUER SAID IT
BACK THEN:

05:59.593 --> 06:01.762
"NO GOOD CAN COME FROM THIS."

06:01.795 --> 06:05.065
- YOU TOLD MR. BAUER
ABOUT THE RAPE?

06:05.098 --> 06:08.101
- YES, HE SAID THAT
MAYBE I WAS CONFUSED,

06:08.135 --> 06:10.538
OR THAT...MY FEELINGS WERE HURT

06:10.571 --> 06:12.940
BECAUSE SHAKIR DIDN'T
SEND FLOWERS.

06:12.973 --> 06:17.445
MR. BAUER SAID THAT IF I KEPT
THE CONVERSATION BETWEEN US,

06:17.478 --> 06:20.448
HE'D RECOMMEND A BONUS
EVERY TIME THAT MY NAME CAME UP.

06:20.481 --> 06:25.653
- AND CARLA, CAN YOU...
PROVE THAT?

06:25.686 --> 06:29.490
- LAST WEEK I GOT $5,000.

06:32.793 --> 06:35.663
- THERE'S REALLY
NOTHING TO TALK ABOUT.

06:35.696 --> 06:38.165
GIRLS THROW THEMSELVES AT SHAKIR
ALL THE TIME.

06:38.198 --> 06:39.800
WHY WOULD HE NEED
TO RAPE SOMEBODY?

06:39.833 --> 06:41.635
- I KNOW WHAT YOU MEAN,
BUT ISN'T IT POSSIBLE

06:41.669 --> 06:43.604
YOU WERE ALSO TRYING
TO PROTECT YOUR COMPANY'S IMAGE?

06:43.637 --> 06:45.639
- MY FATHER VOLUNTEERED
TO SPEAK WITH YOU.

06:45.673 --> 06:48.742
- WE ACTUALLY PREFER
TO SPEAK TO WITNESSES

06:48.776 --> 06:50.611
WITHOUT FAMILY MEMBERS PRESENT.

06:50.644 --> 06:54.147
- CORDELIA IS NOT JUST MY VP,
SHE'S ALSO MY LAWYER,

06:54.181 --> 06:55.716
SO SHE STAYS.

06:55.749 --> 06:58.719
- WANT TO TELL US ABOUT
THE BONUS YOU GAVE CARLA?

06:58.752 --> 07:00.554
- THERE WERE NO PAYMENTS
OF ANY KIND.

07:00.588 --> 07:02.956
- AND WHAT ABOUT
THE EXTRA $5,000 LAST WEEK?

07:02.990 --> 07:04.525
WAS THAT
A PERFORMANCE INCENTIVE?

07:04.558 --> 07:08.862
- ORION BAY IS A FAMILY.
WE TAKE CARE OF EACH OTHER.

07:08.896 --> 07:10.531
WHEN SHE CAME TO ME,

07:10.564 --> 07:13.100
SHE SAID THAT SHE DID NOT
REMEMBER ALL THE DETAILS.

07:13.133 --> 07:15.202
BUT SHE'S A GOOD KID.

07:15.235 --> 07:17.170
MAYBE SHE GOT A LITTLE DRUNK.

07:17.204 --> 07:19.106
I DIDN'T WANT ANY HARD FEELINGS.

07:19.139 --> 07:22.209
- THE PROBLEM IS, IT LOOKS
LIKE YOU'RE COVERING UP A RAPE.

07:22.242 --> 07:23.844
- MY FATHER IS BLAMELESS HERE.

07:23.877 --> 07:26.980
AN UNSTABLE EMPLOYEE MADE
UNSUPPORTED ALLEGATIONS.

07:27.014 --> 07:28.516
IF SHE THOUGHT SHE WAS RAPED,

07:28.549 --> 07:29.983
WHY DIDN'T SHE REPORT THAT
TO THE POLICE?

07:30.017 --> 07:31.184
- SHE HAS NOW.

07:33.220 --> 07:35.689
- SHAKIR IS LIKE A SON TO ME.

07:35.723 --> 07:39.026
HE WOULD NOT DO
SOMETHING LIKE THIS.

07:39.059 --> 07:40.828
LET ME TALK TO THE BOY,
I'LL SEE WHAT HE HAS TO SAY.

07:40.861 --> 07:42.229
- DON'T DO THAT.

07:42.262 --> 07:44.197
IT'S AN OFFICIAL
POLICE INVESTIGATION,

07:44.231 --> 07:47.200
SO ANY CONVERSATION YOU HAVE
WITH SHAKIR, EITHER OF YOU,

07:47.234 --> 07:50.070
COULD BE MISCONSTRUED
AS CONSPIRACY.

07:52.005 --> 07:53.907
- ALL RIGHT, LET'S GO, LET'S GO!
SNAP THAT WRIST, C'MON!

07:53.941 --> 07:56.209
LET'S SEE THAT CROSSOVER,
WHADDYA GOT, WHADDYA GOT? C'MON!

07:56.243 --> 07:58.211
THERE YOU GO. THERE YOU GO!

07:58.245 --> 08:00.247
NEXT TIME, NEXT TIME, LET'S GO,
KEEP IT GOING.

08:00.280 --> 08:03.083
WHADDYA GOT, WHADDYA GOT,
WHADDYA GOT?

08:03.116 --> 08:04.852
THERE YOU GO, GOOD JOB,
GOOD JOB!

08:04.885 --> 08:06.954
- HEY, SHAKIR!
CAN WE TALK TO YOU FOR A MINUTE?

08:09.557 --> 08:10.858
- ALL RIGHT, KEEP IT GOING,
GUYS, KEEP IT GOING,

08:10.891 --> 08:12.225
I'LL BE RIGHT THERE.

08:12.259 --> 08:15.796
- WE JUST NEED TO ASK YOU
A FEW QUESTIONS.

08:15.829 --> 08:17.064
- WHAT'S THIS ABOUT, CARLA?

08:17.097 --> 08:18.732
LOOK, SHE OBVIOUSLY HAS
EMOTIONAL PROBLEMS

08:18.766 --> 08:20.568
BUT I DON'T WANT
TO PRESS ANY CHARGES.

08:20.601 --> 08:22.102
- THAT'S NOT WHAT THIS IS ABOUT.

08:22.135 --> 08:27.541
- SHE'S ACCUSING YOU OF RAPE,
MR. WILKINS.

08:27.575 --> 08:30.277
- LOOK, LIKE I SAID,
SHE HAS EMOTIONAL PROBLEMS,

08:30.310 --> 08:32.112
AND I HOPE SHE GETS
THE HELP SHE NEEDS.

08:32.145 --> 08:33.614
- HMM.

08:33.647 --> 08:35.182
AND HOW LONG HAVE YOU KNOWN HER?

08:35.215 --> 08:36.984
- GIRLS LIKE THAT, THEY COME
AND GO WITH THE COMPANY.

08:37.017 --> 08:38.218
WHAT, MAYBE A YEAR?

08:38.251 --> 08:40.120
- BUT YOU SPENT MEMORIAL DAY
WITH HER, RIGHT?

08:40.153 --> 08:43.791
AND SHE DROVE YOU BACK
TO YOUR HOTEL?

08:43.824 --> 08:46.560
- YEAH, YEAH, UH...
MY TOWN CAR OVERHEATED,

08:46.594 --> 08:48.596
AND SHE DROVE ME BACK
INTO THE CITY.

08:48.629 --> 08:50.931
- TO YOUR HOTEL.
DID ANYTHING HAPPEN?

08:50.964 --> 08:54.034
- WE HAD A DRINK AT THE BAR,
A BITE TO EAT, THEN SHE LEFT.

08:54.067 --> 08:55.102
- AND THAT'S IT.

08:55.135 --> 08:56.203
- YEAH.

08:56.236 --> 08:58.038
- BECAUSE, UM...

08:58.071 --> 08:59.272
SHE SAYS YOU DRUGGED HER, YOU
TOOK HER BACK UP TO YOUR ROOM,

08:59.306 --> 09:01.809
AND YOU RAPED HER.

09:01.842 --> 09:03.176
- THAT'S INSANE.
THAT DID NOT HAPPEN.

09:03.210 --> 09:04.978
- THEN WHY WOULD SHE SAY IT DID?

09:05.012 --> 09:06.079
- BUT...THIS...

09:06.113 --> 09:07.314
THIS IS NOTHING BUT A SHAKEDOWN.

09:07.347 --> 09:08.849
- SHE CAME AT YOU FOR MONEY?

09:08.882 --> 09:10.984
- NO...BUT SHE WILL.

09:11.018 --> 09:13.186
I'M GOING THROUGH A DIVORCE
RIGHT NOW--A CUSTODY BATTLE.

09:13.220 --> 09:14.822
IT'S IN THE PAPERS.
SHE KNOWS ABOUT IT.

09:14.855 --> 09:16.624
- YEAH, WE GET THAT.

09:16.657 --> 09:20.193
- LOOK, I FEEL BADLY
FOR THIS GIRL.

09:20.227 --> 09:22.162
I'M TRYING
NOT TO OVERREACT HERE,

09:22.195 --> 09:24.264
BUT IF ANYONE WAS ASSAULTED IT
WAS ME, IN THAT ELEVATOR.

09:24.297 --> 09:26.033
- YOU WANT TO PRESS CHARGES,
THEN?

09:30.203 --> 09:32.072
- YEAH, MAYBE I SHOULD TALK TO
MY LAWYER AT THIS POINT,

09:32.105 --> 09:33.974
TO PROTECT MYSELF, OKAY?

09:34.007 --> 09:36.076
IN THE MEANTIME I HAVE
TO GET BACK TO THESE KIDS.

09:36.109 --> 09:38.979
- SHAKIR, HOW LONG
YOU GONNA BE IN TOWN?

09:39.012 --> 09:41.114
- FEW MORE EVENTS,
JUST FOR THE WEEK.

09:41.148 --> 09:45.218
- 'CAUSE IF YOU LEAVE, YOU NEED
TO TELL US WHERE YOU'RE GOING.

09:52.292 --> 09:54.094
- LOOK, SOMETHING SET CARLA OFF.

09:54.127 --> 09:56.029
- IT HAPPENED THREE MONTHS AGO.

09:56.063 --> 09:58.098
BUT SHE WAITS UNTIL ALL
THE HOTEL VIDEO'S BEEN ERASED

09:58.131 --> 10:00.067
AND SHE'S GOT
A LOBBY FULL OF PRESS?

10:00.100 --> 10:02.269
- PUTTING ON A SHOW
FOR THE SECURITY CAMERAS.

10:02.302 --> 10:05.072
SHAKIR THINKS IT'S A SHAKEDOWN.
HE'S GOING THROUGH A DIVORCE.

10:05.105 --> 10:06.907
- COME ON, GUYS, I DON'T WANT TO
HEAR THAT WOMEN LIE,

10:06.940 --> 10:08.408
AND THAT SHAKIR IS A HERO

10:08.441 --> 10:10.177
AND HE NEVER COULD HAVE DONE
SUCH A THING.

10:10.210 --> 10:13.180
THIS IS SVU, AND WE
TAKE DISCLOSURES SERIOUSLY.

10:13.213 --> 10:14.882
- COPY THAT, SERGEANT, BUT...

10:14.915 --> 10:16.684
FOR WHAT IT'S WORTH?

10:16.717 --> 10:19.052
SHAKIR'S BEEN A PUBLIC FIGURE
FOR WHAT, 20 YEARS?

10:19.086 --> 10:21.188
THERE'S NEVER BEEN A WHISPER
ABOUT ANYTHING LIKE THIS,

10:21.221 --> 10:22.723
THIS IS JUST LIKE
COMING OUT OF NOWHERE.

10:22.756 --> 10:24.825
- AND, THIS GIRL CAN'T REMEMBER
ANY DETAILS.

10:24.858 --> 10:26.093
- EXACTLY.
- GUYS...

10:26.126 --> 10:29.362
WE'VE HAD CASES
WHERE ATHLETES DRUG WOMEN.

10:29.396 --> 10:31.231
RAWLINS, ARE YOU WITH US?

10:31.264 --> 10:35.035
- UH...YEAH...IT'S...
MY OLD CAPTAIN IN ATLANTA.

10:35.068 --> 10:39.239
A GIRL DOWN THERE CLAIMS THAT
SHAKIR DID THE SAME THING TO HER

10:39.272 --> 10:40.440
AFTER SEEING HIM ON THE NEWS.

10:40.473 --> 10:42.209
- AH.
THEY'RE PILING ON NOW, HUH?

10:42.242 --> 10:45.746
- OKAY, SO, GO GET ON A PLANE
AND TALK TO THE GIRL.

10:45.779 --> 10:49.116
AND, UH, DON'T LET
YOUR HERO WORSHIP BLIND YOU.

10:49.149 --> 10:50.984
- WILL DO.

10:51.018 --> 10:54.087
MAYBE I'LL CHECK IN
ON MY MOM WHILE I'M THERE.

10:56.957 --> 10:59.226
- SO YOU GONNA SEE MOM
WHILE YOU'RE HERE?

10:59.259 --> 11:01.194
- NO...
I DON'T KNOW.

11:02.195 --> 11:03.764
TELL ME ABOUT THIS VICTIM.

11:03.797 --> 11:06.033
- WELL, I DON'T KNOW
THAT SHE IS ONE.

11:06.066 --> 11:09.236
SHE CLAIMS SHAKIR WILKINS
RAPED HER OVER SIX MONTHS AGO.

11:09.269 --> 11:11.772
NO OUTCRY, NO PHYSICAL EVIDENCE.

11:11.805 --> 11:14.708
WE'RE NOT PURSUING.
- OKAY, SO...

11:14.742 --> 11:16.243
WHY'D YOU CALL ME?

11:16.276 --> 11:19.079
- THOUGHT YOU'D WANT TO KNOW.

11:19.112 --> 11:23.150
MAYBE I...JUST WANTED
AN EXCUSE.

11:23.183 --> 11:25.352
- YOU AND YOUR WIFE SEPARATED?
AGAIN?

11:25.385 --> 11:26.787
- THIS TIME IT'S FOR GOOD.

11:26.820 --> 11:28.956
LITTLE GIRL'S IN COLLEGE, SO...

11:28.989 --> 11:30.223
YOU UP FOR A BEER LATER?

11:30.257 --> 11:31.825
- I GOTTA TAKE A RAIN CHECK
ON THAT.

11:31.859 --> 11:34.795
I GOTTA CATCH THE 5:00 TODAY,
BACK TO NEW YORK.

11:34.828 --> 11:36.129
THEY WORK YOU HARD UP THERE.

11:36.163 --> 11:38.766
- OH.
NEXT TIME.

11:38.799 --> 11:41.101
- HEY, IS THE DEPUTY CHIEF IN?

11:41.134 --> 11:42.803
- YOU JUST MISSED HIM.

11:42.836 --> 11:44.938
HE SAID HE KNEW YOU WERE COMING
AND HE SENDS HIS REGARDS.

11:44.972 --> 11:47.908
- HMM.

11:47.941 --> 11:51.111
- I WAS SHAKIR'S STYLIST
ON A SHOOT.

11:51.144 --> 11:54.147
I WAS THRILLED TO MEET HIM...

11:54.181 --> 11:56.183
AT FIRST.

11:56.216 --> 12:01.288
- TELL ME WHAT HAPPENED,
MACIE-LYNN.

12:01.321 --> 12:04.825
- HE INVITED ME
TO HIS HOTEL AFTER.

12:05.859 --> 12:09.897
WE HAD SOME WINE.

12:12.232 --> 12:14.835
THE NEXT THING I REMEMBER...

12:14.868 --> 12:16.970
I WAS IN HIS BED,

12:18.305 --> 12:21.208
NAKED.

12:23.076 --> 12:26.513
HE RAPED ME,
JUST LIKE THAT OTHER GIRL SAID.

12:26.546 --> 12:28.181
- DID YOU TELL ANYONE?

12:28.215 --> 12:29.850
- NO.

12:29.883 --> 12:31.985
ATLANTA'S A SMALL TOWN,
PEOPLE TALK.

12:32.019 --> 12:34.788
- YEAH...THEY DO.

12:34.822 --> 12:39.026
- SO, I, UM...
I CALLED MR. BAUER.

12:39.059 --> 12:41.261
I'D MET HIM
AT SOME EVENTS DOWN HERE.

12:41.294 --> 12:44.865
HE TOLD ME THE SAME THING
THAT CAPTAIN OUT THERE SAID,

12:44.898 --> 12:49.269
THAT NO GOOD WILL COME
FROM MAKING A COMPLAINT.

12:49.302 --> 12:51.271
- UM...

12:51.304 --> 12:56.009
DID MR. BAUER OFFER
ANY KIND OF OTHER HELP AT ALL?

12:58.178 --> 13:00.280
- HE SAID HE DIDN'T WANT
HARD FEELINGS,

13:00.313 --> 13:05.552
SO IF I COULD LET IT GO,
HE'D SEE TO IT I GOT A BONUS.

13:07.888 --> 13:11.859
I SUPPORT MY FAMILY,
MY DADDY LOST HIS JOB...

13:11.892 --> 13:15.128
I NEEDED THE MONEY.

13:17.397 --> 13:21.168
- SO I GAVE THIS MARCIE GIRL
FIVE GRAND.

13:21.201 --> 13:23.336
SHE HAD NO MEMORY
OF WHAT HAPPENED.

13:23.370 --> 13:26.206
