CARLA TOLD.

13:26.239 --> 13:28.541
- BUT...YOU HADN'T HEARD
CARLA'S STORY YET,

13:28.575 --> 13:32.412
AND MACIE-LYNN
WAS SIX MONTHS AGO.

13:32.445 --> 13:34.381
- WELL, I MAY HAVE
THE TIMELINE CONFUSED--

13:34.414 --> 13:36.349
- MY FATHER RUNS
A MULTI-BILLION DOLLAR COMPANY

13:36.383 --> 13:39.286
FIELDING HUNDREDS OF EMAILS
AND PHONE CALLS A DAY.

13:39.319 --> 13:41.955
YOU CAN'T EXPECT HIM TO REMEMBER
WHO SAID WHAT WHEN.

13:41.989 --> 13:43.891
- YEAH. BUT YOU'D REMEMBER

13:43.924 --> 13:46.193
IF SOMEBODY ELSE CAME TO YOU
ABOUT SHAKIR, RIGHT?

13:46.226 --> 13:48.295
- HOW'S THAT?
- MR. BAUER?

13:48.328 --> 13:50.563
YOU'RE LOOKING AT
WITNESS BRIBERY.

13:50.597 --> 13:52.099
THINK HARD.

13:52.132 --> 13:53.934
- OKAY, ACTUALLY,
WE ARE DONE HERE.

13:53.967 --> 13:55.535
DAD?
- NO, NO, NO.

13:57.170 --> 13:59.206
THERE WAS A GOLD DIGGER,

13:59.239 --> 14:00.473
A BLACK GIRL...

14:00.507 --> 14:03.010
WORKS IN RETAIL.

14:03.043 --> 14:05.979
