A WORD SHE SAID.

14:08.648 --> 14:10.150
- HEY, YOU'RE TIANA?

14:10.183 --> 14:15.288
WE NEED TO TALK TO YOU
ABOUT SHAKIR.

14:15.322 --> 14:17.891
- THIS ABOUT THAT GIRL WHO
WENT OFF ON HIM IN THE ELEVATOR?

14:17.925 --> 14:19.626
- MM-HMM.

14:23.463 --> 14:26.466
- I LIKE WORKING HERE.
I DON'T WANT NO PART OF THIS.

14:26.499 --> 14:27.935
- SO YOU THINK IF YOU TALK
TO THE POLICE,

14:27.968 --> 14:30.037
YOU'RE GONNA LOSE YOUR JOB?

14:30.070 --> 14:33.206
- MR. BAUER SAID SHAKIR
IS THE GOLDEN GOOSE,

14:33.240 --> 14:35.943
ROLE MODEL FOR MY COMMUNITY.

14:35.976 --> 14:39.679
LOOK AROUND, WE ALL HAVE
OUR JOBS BECAUSE OF SHAKIR.

14:39.712 --> 14:42.115
I'M ON A STORE MANAGER TRACK
HERE.

14:42.149 --> 14:47.387
- AND HE TOLD YOU THAT
AFTER YOU WENT TO HIM?

14:48.455 --> 14:51.424
MR. BAUER...SENT US HERE.

14:51.458 --> 14:53.260
- HE DID?

14:54.962 --> 14:59.399
- LISTEN, HONEY,
FROM PERSONAL EXPERIENCE?

14:59.432 --> 15:04.637
PRETENDING SOMETHING DIDN'T
HAPPEN DOESN'T MAKE IT GO AWAY.

15:18.051 --> 15:18.251
.

15:18.285 --> 15:19.119
- I'M SORRY, WHO ARE WE
TALKING ABOUT NOW?

15:20.620 --> 15:21.588
- TIANA RAYNES.
SHARKWEAR SALESGIRL.

15:21.621 --> 15:23.256
- AND SHE KEPT HER PANTIES?

15:23.290 --> 15:24.457
- YEAH, THERE WAS SEMEN ON THEM
AND HER DRESS.

15:24.491 --> 15:25.959
- BETTER THAN AN AUTOGRAPH.

15:25.993 --> 15:27.360
- WHEN DOES SHE ALLEGE
THIS TOOK PLACE?

15:27.394 --> 15:28.561
- YOU WERE IN HER STORE

15:28.595 --> 15:30.163
FOR A MARCH MADNESS EVENT,
MR. WILKINS.

15:30.197 --> 15:31.965
- I WAS EVERYWHERE
FOR MARCH MADNESS.

15:31.999 --> 15:33.233
16 CITIES IN 16 DAYS.

15:33.266 --> 15:36.336
- THIS WAS IN THE SHARKWEAR
FLAGSHIP STORE.

15:36.369 --> 15:40.107
TIANA TOOK A SELFIE WITH YOU
AND YOUR CUTOUT.

15:40.140 --> 15:41.641
THAT'S HER, THAT'S THE DRESS.

15:41.674 --> 15:43.143
- OKAY, SHE MET HIM.

15:43.176 --> 15:44.611
- WELL, SHE SAYS
HE DID MORE THAN THAT,

15:44.644 --> 15:47.347
SO WE ARE GOING TO NEED
A DNA SAMPLE TODAY, MR. WILKINS.

15:47.380 --> 15:49.182
- JUST A MINUTE. SHAKIR--
- NO, NO, LOOK,

15:49.216 --> 15:52.385
I WANNA BE
TOTALLY STRAIGHT HERE.

15:54.687 --> 15:56.689
I WAS IN A BAD PLACE.

15:56.723 --> 15:58.625
I JUST LOST MY MARRIAGE.

15:58.658 --> 16:00.227
AND MY WIFE AND I SEPARATED
ON NEW YEAR'S,

16:00.260 --> 16:03.363
AND YES, I'VE BEEN
DATING SINCE.

16:03.396 --> 16:05.365
- AND YOU "DATED"
TIANA RAYNES?

16:05.398 --> 16:07.067
- NO, HOOKED UP.

16:07.100 --> 16:10.037
ONE TIME, AFTER HOURS,
IN A--A DRESSING ROOM,

16:10.070 --> 16:13.040
AND IT WAS HER IDEA.
- THAT'S NOT HER STORY.

16:13.073 --> 16:15.375
SHE TOLD ME YOU DRUGGED HER,
AND SHE WOKE UP THE NEXT MORNING

16:15.408 --> 16:17.244
IN THE STORE,
HER DRESS STAINED.

16:17.277 --> 16:19.346
- SHE SAYS THIS NOW,
FIVE MONTHS LATER?

16:19.379 --> 16:21.414
AND SHE JUST HAPPENED
TO SAVE THE PANTIES?

16:21.448 --> 16:23.016
THIS IS WELL-TIMED BLACKMAIL.

16:23.050 --> 16:24.417
- LOOK, SHE'S LYING
ABOUT THE RAPE.

16:24.451 --> 16:25.585
- YEAH, LIKE...

16:25.618 --> 16:28.521
CARLA? HMM?
LIKE MACIE-LYNN?

16:28.555 --> 16:30.323
THEY ALL SAY THAT YOU BOUGHT
THEM A DRINK,

16:30.357 --> 16:32.025
AND THE NEXT THING
THEY REMEMBER,

16:32.059 --> 16:33.360
THEY WERE NAKED,
AND THEY HAD BEEN VIOLATED!

16:33.393 --> 16:36.329
- THEY ARE LYING TOO!
- ABOUT WHAT?

16:36.363 --> 16:38.465
TIANA'S LYING
ABOUT BEING RAPED?

16:38.498 --> 16:40.333
BUT YOU DID HAVE SEX WITH HER,

16:40.367 --> 16:44.104
AND THE OTHER TWO, THEY'RE
LYING ABOUT EVERYTHING?

16:44.137 --> 16:47.807
- OKAY, OKAY, I DON'T KNOW
WHAT'S GOING ON HERE,

16:47.840 --> 16:50.643
BUT CARLA, AND THE OTHER ONE--
- MACIE-LYNN?

16:52.145 --> 16:54.347
- I MAY HAVE HAD SEX
WITH THEM ALSO.

16:54.381 --> 16:56.249
- AND IF YOU DID,
IT WAS CONSENSUAL,

16:56.283 --> 16:57.484
ISN'T THAT RIGHT, SHAKIR?

16:57.517 --> 16:59.386
- YES, ABSOLUTELY.

16:59.419 --> 17:03.156
I MEAN, SO I WASN'T ALL WARM
AND CUDDLY AFTERWARDS.

17:03.190 --> 17:04.757
I LIKE SLEEPING ALONE.

17:04.791 --> 17:06.459
YOU KNOW,
SPENDING THE NIGHT, SPOONING,

17:06.493 --> 17:08.428
IT'S NOT PART OF
THE SHAKIR WILKINS EXPERIENCE.

17:08.461 --> 17:11.131
- CAN'T BLAME YOU THERE.

17:11.164 --> 17:12.699
NOW BY THE WAY,
DO YOU HAVE A PRESCRIPTION

17:12.732 --> 17:14.234
FOR AMBIEN OR XANAX?

17:14.267 --> 17:17.270
- YES, OF COURSE I DO.

17:17.304 --> 17:18.438
I CAN'T SLEEP MOST NIGHTS

17:18.471 --> 17:22.242
BECAUSE MY WIFE
IS TRYING TO TAKE MY SON.

17:22.275 --> 17:25.245
AND THAT'S WHY I COULDN'T
ADMIT TO THE SEX.

17:25.278 --> 17:27.614
SHE WILL CRUCIFY ME WITH IT
IN THE CUSTODY BATTLE.

17:27.647 --> 17:29.449
- YOU'VE GOT BIGGER PROBLEMS
THAN A CUSTODY BATTLE,

17:29.482 --> 17:30.750
MR. WILKINS.

17:36.289 --> 17:37.624
- OKAY, NOW SHAKIR IS SAYING

17:37.657 --> 17:39.559
HE DID HAVE SEX WITH ALL THREE
OF THEM?

17:39.592 --> 17:41.261
- LET ME GUESS,
IT WAS CONSENSUAL.

17:41.294 --> 17:42.795
- IT'S POSSIBLE.

17:42.829 --> 17:45.198
I HAD TWO GIRLS CLAIM
THEIR DAD MOLESTED THEM,

17:45.232 --> 17:46.833
JUST TO GET HIM TO PAY
THEIR STUDENT LOANS OFF.

17:46.866 --> 17:49.869
- NO RAPE KITS.
NO OUTCRY AT THE TIME.

17:49.902 --> 17:51.504
BARBA'S REALLY GONNA GO FORWARD
WITH THIS?

17:51.538 --> 17:53.606
- GIVE IT A REST, GUYS.

17:53.640 --> 17:56.176
I DIDN'T WANT
TO BELIEVE IT EITHER.

17:56.209 --> 17:58.311
BUT WE'VE GOT
THREE CONSISTENT STORIES,

17:58.345 --> 18:00.413
AND THERE'S NO EVIDENCE THAT
THE WOMEN COMPARED NOTES--

18:00.447 --> 18:01.481
- THEY MAY BE JUST AFTER MONEY.

18:01.514 --> 18:03.250
THEY ALREADY GOT IT FROM BAUER.

18:03.283 --> 18:05.485
- TO KEEP QUIET
ABOUT BEING ASSAULTED.

18:05.518 --> 18:07.387
- YOU WANT AN OUTCRY WITNESS?

18:07.420 --> 18:09.422
BAUER'S YOUR GUY.
- GOOD LUCK!

18:09.456 --> 18:11.624
- YOU THINK ORION BAUER'S
GONNA TANK SHAKIR? MM-MM.

18:11.658 --> 18:14.494
I'M PREDICTING HEALTH PROBLEMS,
MINI STROKE, SOMETHING.

18:14.527 --> 18:16.696
- WE HAVE HIM
ON WITNESS BRIBERY CHARGES.

18:16.729 --> 18:18.398
THAT GIVES US LEVERAGE.
IN THE MEANTIME,

18:18.431 --> 18:20.433
LET'S VET
THE THREE COMPLAINANTS.

18:20.467 --> 18:22.569
MONEY ISSUES,
PERSONAL HISTORIES,

18:22.602 --> 18:25.272
AND ANY PREVIOUS
FALSE ACCUSATIONS.

18:25.305 --> 18:28.441
- NO, NO.
I WON'T TESTIFY AGAINST SHAKIR!

18:28.475 --> 18:30.343
IT'S NOT JUST THE MONEY,
HE'S BEEN LOYAL!

18:30.377 --> 18:32.312
HAVE YOU READ HIS AUTOBIOGRAPHY?

18:32.345 --> 18:34.447
I DON'T EVEN KNOW IF HE'S
READ IT, BUT THE POINT IS:

18:34.481 --> 18:36.249
HE'S AN INSPIRING STORY.

18:36.283 --> 18:38.718
- HEY, DAD, LISTEN,
WE'RE ON THEIR COURT NOW.

18:38.751 --> 18:40.187
ALL RIGHT?

18:40.220 --> 18:42.389
LET US LISTEN TO WHAT THEY HAVE
TO SAY.

18:42.422 --> 18:45.258
- MR. BAUER, WE'VE GOT
THREE CREDIBLE VICS

18:45.292 --> 18:46.893
WITH CONSISTENT STORIES.

18:46.926 --> 18:48.328
YOU'RE AN OUTCRY WITNESS
IN ALL THREE CASES.

18:48.361 --> 18:49.629
- WHAT THE HELL DOES THAT MEAN?

18:49.662 --> 18:51.731
- THAT MEANS THAT THEY ALL
CAME TO YOU, DAD.

18:51.764 --> 18:54.301
- BECAUSE I'M LIKE A FATHER
TO EVERYONE IN THIS COMPANY.

18:54.334 --> 18:55.768
- AND LIKE A FATHER,
WHEN THEY CAME TO YOU

18:55.802 --> 18:58.371
THEY SAID THEY'D BEEN ATTACKED,
YOU GAVE THEM MONEY,

18:58.405 --> 19:00.473
AND YOU TOLD THEM TO KEEP QUIET.

19:00.507 --> 19:01.574
YOU'RE ON THE HOOK HERE.

19:01.608 --> 19:03.310
ASK YOUR DAUGHTER.

19:03.343 --> 19:05.912
- IF MY FATHER TESTIFIES
TO WHAT THESE WOMEN SAID,

19:05.945 --> 19:08.315
IS THAT IN EXCHANGE FOR CHARGES
NOT BEING FILED AGAINST HIM?

19:08.348 --> 19:09.949
- CHARGES FOR WHAT?

19:09.982 --> 19:12.652
- YOU PAID THEM, MR. BAUER!
- THOSE WERE BONUSES.

19:12.685 --> 19:14.921
- A WEEK BEFORE SHAKIR'S
CONTRACT WAS TO BE RENEWED?

19:14.954 --> 19:16.756
- WE RENEWED HIS CONTRACT
TWO MONTHS AGO.

19:16.789 --> 19:18.391
THE ONLY REASON
WE KEPT IT SECRET

19:18.425 --> 19:20.393
IS BECAUSE WE WANTED
TO ANNOUNCE IN THE FALL.

19:20.427 --> 19:23.396
- DAD, DAD...
LISTEN.

19:23.430 --> 19:26.266
AS PAINFUL AS THIS IS,

19:26.299 --> 19:28.868
YOU HAVE GOT TO LET SHAKIR GO.

19:28.901 --> 19:31.371
NO MATTER WHAT HAPPENS,

19:31.404 --> 19:34.274
HE CANNOT WORK FOR ORION BAY
ANYMORE.

19:34.307 --> 19:36.609
DO YOU HEAR ME?

19:38.311 --> 19:41.981
I JUST...I...

19:42.014 --> 19:43.783
I DIDN'T SEE THIS COMING.

19:43.816 --> 19:45.652
- I KNOW.

19:47.320 --> 19:50.590
- YOU MUST THINK
I'M AN OLD FOOL.

19:50.623 --> 19:53.693
- NO, DADDY.
NO, I DON'T.

19:58.465 --> 20:00.700
- NOBODY TOLD ME
I'D HAVE TO TESTIFY.

20:00.733 --> 20:02.269
- YOU MIGHT.

20:02.302 --> 20:04.271
OUR D.A. IS GOING TO ARGUE THAT
WHAT HAPPENED TO YOU

20:04.304 --> 20:06.339
IS PART OF A PATTERN.

20:08.308 --> 20:09.742
- IS SHAKIR GONNA BE THERE?

20:09.776 --> 20:12.412
- YEAH.

20:12.445 --> 20:13.980
- LIKE I TOLD
THAT GIRL DETECTIVE,

20:14.013 --> 20:15.915
I DON'T REMEMBER TOO MUCH OF IT.

20:15.948 --> 20:17.650
- OKAY.

20:17.684 --> 20:20.753
LET'S JUST START WITH
THE PART THAT YOU DO REMEMBER.

20:20.787 --> 20:22.355
- YOU NEED ME TO TESTIFY?

20:22.389 --> 20:24.891
- UNDER OATH.
IS THAT A PROBLEM?

20:24.924 --> 20:28.395
- NO. NO, IT'S JUST I--
WELL, I HEARD--

20:28.428 --> 20:31.464
THE OTHER GIRL, THE BLACK ONE,
SHE SAVED HER PANTIES.

20:31.498 --> 20:33.600
- WHERE DID YOU HEAR THAT?

20:33.633 --> 20:36.336
- UM, I HEARD CORDELIA
ON HER CELL.

20:36.369 --> 20:38.371
SHE WAS TALKING TO SHAKIR.
SHE WAS VERY UPSET.

20:38.405 --> 20:40.573
- YEAH, THAT EVIDENCE IS
A START, CARLA,

20:40.607 --> 20:44.344
BUT YOU KNOW, IF THERE'S
ANYTHING THAT YOU HAVE

20:44.377 --> 20:47.647
OR ANYTHING THAT YOU COULD GET
TO CORROBORATE YOUR STORY,

20:47.680 --> 20:51.017
THAT WOULD--
THAT'D BE A BIG HELP.

21:04.464 --> 21:06.433
- I'M GLAD YOU CALLED.

21:07.434 --> 21:08.968
- YOU ARE?

21:09.001 --> 21:13.039
- I'M SORRY IF I HURT YOU,

21:13.072 --> 21:17.377
AND I WANT TO MAKE THIS RIGHT,
BEFORE WE ALL GET HURT.

21:17.410 --> 21:20.012
- ALL?
ARE YOU THREATENING ME?

21:20.046 --> 21:22.349
I THOUGHT THAT
WE COULD JUST TALK.

21:22.382 --> 21:25.652
- WE BOTH KNOW I'M NOT THE ONLY
ATHLETE YOU'VE BEEN WITH.

21:27.687 --> 21:31.391
LISTEN, YOU TAKE THE STAND...

21:31.424 --> 21:33.426
IT'S FAIR GAME.

21:35.462 --> 21:37.797
BUT WE DON'T HAVE
TO GO DOWN THAT ROAD.

21:37.830 --> 21:40.833
WE CAN MAKE ALL THIS GO AWAY.

21:40.867 --> 21:42.702
YOU CAN START OVER.

21:42.735 --> 21:46.038
YOU KNOW, MAYBE GET YOURSELF
A CONDO IN THE CITY,

21:46.072 --> 21:48.375
BUT IT'S YOUR CHOICE, CARLA.
- A CONTROLLED MEET?

21:48.408 --> 21:50.410
YOU CAN'T DO THAT ONCE HE'S
REPRESENTED BY COUNSEL.

21:50.443 --> 21:51.411
- WASN'T OUR IDEA.
THIS IS ALL HER.

21:51.444 --> 21:52.879
IT'S HER PHONE.

21:52.912 --> 21:54.614
- UH-HUH, AND SECOND OF ALL,
IT'S NOT PROBATIVE.

21:54.647 --> 21:56.583
- PLEADING IN THE ALTERNATIVE,
NEVER A SIGN OF STRENGTH.

21:56.616 --> 21:58.451
- I WAS JUST TRYING TO FIND OUT
WHY SHE WAS LYING,

21:58.485 --> 21:59.819
WHAT SHE WANTED.
- SHAKIR, YOU'VE DONE--

21:59.852 --> 22:03.456
- SHAKIR WILKINS
IS NOT A RAPIST!

22:03.490 --> 22:05.091
- AND YOU'LL GET THE OPPORTUNITY
TO TELL YOUR SIDE OF THE STORY

22:05.124 --> 22:07.594
TO THE JURY.

22:09.496 --> 22:11.097
- SHAKIR WILKINS,

22:11.130 --> 22:12.632
YOU'RE UNDER ARREST.

22:12.665 --> 22:14.434
YOU HAVE THE RIGHT
TO REMAIN SILENT.

22:14.467 --> 22:16.603
ANYTHING YOU SAY CAN AND WILL
BE HELD AGAINST YOU

22:25.645 --> 22:25.845
.

22:25.878 --> 22:26.846
- IT IS WITH A HEAVY HEART
THAT I ANNOUNCE THAT...

22:28.515 --> 22:30.517
ORION BAY IS TERMINATING
ITS RELATIONSHIP

22:30.550 --> 22:34.687
WITH SHAKIR WILKINS
EFFECTIVE IMMEDIATELY.

22:34.721 --> 22:36.055
- SHAKIR!
[reporters yelling]

22:36.088 --> 22:40.627
- HE IS, LIKE EVERYONE,
ENTITLED TO DUE PROCESS.

22:40.660 --> 22:42.929
ONLY MR. WILKINS
AND THESE WOMEN KNOW

22:42.962 --> 22:47.133
WHAT REALLY TRANSPIRED
BEHIND CLOSED DOORS.

22:47.166 --> 22:50.403
BUT THE LACK OF JUDGMENT FOR
A MARRIED MAN TO BE ALONE,

22:50.437 --> 22:54.907
IN A ROOM, WITH THREE
DIFFERENT WOMEN AT LATE HOURS

22:54.941 --> 22:56.976
IS UNDENIABLE.

22:57.009 --> 23:00.613
WE HAVE ALWAYS CELEBRATED
ROLE MODELS,

23:00.647 --> 23:02.515
BUT NO MATTER WHAT
THE COURT DECIDES,

23:02.549 --> 23:05.785
MR. WILKINS HAS FORFEITED
THE PRIVILEGE

23:05.818 --> 23:09.756
OF REPRESENTING ORION BAY.

23:09.789 --> 23:11.057
THANK YOU.

23:13.059 --> 23:15.428
- AND WHEN THE THIRD WOMAN,
TIANA RAYNES, CAME TO YOU

23:15.462 --> 23:17.564
AND SAID SHAKIR WILKINS
HAD RAPED HER,

23:17.597 --> 23:20.032
DID YOU PROMISE HER A BONUS?
- YES, I DID.

23:20.066 --> 23:25.104
- CAN YOU TELL THE JURY WHY YOU
OFFERED THESE WOMEN BONUSES,

23:25.137 --> 23:30.877
WHICH MAY APPEAR TO SOME
AS BUYING THEIR SILENCE?

23:30.910 --> 23:32.879
- I TAKE NO JOY IN THIS.

23:32.912 --> 23:36.516
I'VE HAD A LONG-TERM
RELATIONSHIP WITH MR. WILKINS.

23:36.549 --> 23:39.919
