MY KNOWLEDGE OF HIM

23:39.952 --> 23:41.921
WITH WHAT THESE WOMEN
WERE SAYING.

23:41.954 --> 23:45.091
AT THE TIME, I BELIEVED THAT
THESE WERE FALSE ALLEGATIONS.

23:45.124 --> 23:46.993
