23:52.732 --> 23:55.067
AND THESE OTHER GIRLS...

23:55.101 --> 23:57.770
THERE'S A SAYING:
WHEN THREE PEOPLE AT A PARTY

23:57.804 --> 24:01.808
TELL YOU YOU'RE DRUNK,
DON'T DRIVE HOME.

24:01.841 --> 24:03.175
- THANK YOU, MR. BAUER.

