- I'M TESTIFYING HERE TODAY
BECAUSE I MADE A WRONG DECISION,

24:18.658 --> 24:19.992
AND FOR THAT, I APOLOGIZE.

24:20.026 --> 24:21.694
- BUT NO CHARGES
HAVE BEEN FILED.

24:21.728 --> 24:22.962
- CORRECT.

24:22.995 --> 24:26.599
- AT THE TIME THESE COMPLAINANTS
CAME FORWARD,

24:26.633 --> 24:27.934
DID YOU BELIEVE THEIR STORIES?

24:27.967 --> 24:30.970
- NO, I DID NOT.
I SIMPLY COULDN'T THINK

24:31.003 --> 24:33.105
THAT THE MAN I KNEW
WAS CAPABLE OF DOING

24:33.139 --> 24:34.974
THE THINGS THEY SAID
HE WAS DOING.

24:35.007 --> 24:37.777
- BUT NOW YOU DO BELIEVE
THAT SHAKIR WILKINS

24:37.810 --> 24:39.912
ASSAULTED THESE THREE WOMEN?

24:39.946 --> 24:41.848
- YES, I DO.

24:41.881 --> 24:44.751
AS I SAID, AFTER THAT SCENE IN
THE ELEVATOR WITH CARLA,

24:44.784 --> 24:48.020
REPLAYING ALL THEIR WORDS
WITHOUT BLINDERS ON,

24:48.054 --> 24:50.857
SO GOD HELP ME,
YES, I DO.

24:50.890 --> 24:53.760
- DOES THE SUDDEN CHANGE
IN YOUR BELIEFS

24:53.793 --> 24:55.895
GIVE YOU THE RIGHT TO INVOKE
THE MORALS CLAUSE

24:55.928 --> 24:58.731
AND TERMINATE YOUR CONTRACT
WITH MR. WILKINS,

24:58.765 --> 25:02.001
SAVING YOUR COMPANY ROUGHLY
HALF A BILLION DOLLARS?

25:02.034 --> 25:04.871
- ROUGHLY, YES, BUT THAT'S
