WITH A LITTLE BLACK BABY
CLINGING ONTO YOU?

37:36.722 --> 37:38.690
AND WHEN HE GOES TO DALTON?

37:38.724 --> 37:39.991
WHAT DO YOU THINK THEY'RE
GONNA SAY?

37:40.025 --> 37:42.494
"OH, HERE COMES
THE SCHOLARSHIP BOY?"

37:42.528 --> 37:43.962
- YOU CAN'T SAY THESE THINGS,
DADDY.

37:43.995 --> 37:45.431
- OH, YES, I CAN.
- YOU CAN'T SAY THESE THINGS.

37:45.464 --> 37:47.466
YES, I CAN! THESE PEOPLE COME
INTO OUR HOMES.

37:47.499 --> 37:49.034
THEY COME INTO OUR FAMILIES.

37:49.067 --> 37:51.537
THEY ARE ANIMALS.

37:51.570 --> 37:53.339
I DID WHAT I HAD TO DO
TO PROTECT YOU

37:53.372 --> 37:55.641
FROM MAKING THE BIGGEST
MISTAKE--

37:55.674 --> 37:57.309
- ANIMALS?

37:57.343 --> 37:58.844
HE MAKES HIS LIVING
OFF ATHLETES,

37:58.877 --> 38:01.413
AND HE TALKS LIKE THAT?
- WOW.

38:01.447 --> 38:05.651
LOOK, HE'S GOTTA BE SENILE,
OR CRAZY, OR...BOTH

38:05.684 --> 38:07.453
- YEAH, I FEEL BAD FOR CORDELIA.

38:07.486 --> 38:10.356
HER FATHER'S A NARCISSIST.
SHE FELL FOR ANOTHER ONE.

38:10.389 --> 38:12.491
SHE NEVER HAD A CHANCE.
- AND HOW DID WE...

38:12.524 --> 38:13.992
GET THIS TAPE?

38:14.025 --> 38:16.362
- I CAN'T TELL YOU.
AND I HAD TO PROMISE

38:16.395 --> 38:19.365
IT WOULDN'T BE USED
AGAINST MR. BAUER.

38:19.398 --> 38:21.700
BUT WE KNOW WHAT THIS MEANS.

38:23.935 --> 38:25.671
- IN LIGHT OF NEW EVIDENCE,
WE'RE ASKING

38:25.704 --> 38:28.907
FOR AN IMMEDIATE DISMISSAL
OF ALL CHARGES, YOUR HONOR.

38:28.940 --> 38:30.476
- MR. BARBA?

38:30.509 --> 38:33.078
- THE PEOPLE HAVE NO OBJECTION.

38:33.111 --> 38:35.113
- SO ORDERED.

38:35.146 --> 38:37.583
MR. WILKINS,
YOU ARE FREE TO GO.

38:46.725 --> 38:49.461
- WIN SOME, LOSE SOME,
MR. BARBA.

38:49.495 --> 38:50.896
NICE TIE.

38:58.470 --> 39:02.774
- I'M GONNA GO UPSTAIRS
AND...DUCK CALLS.

39:02.808 --> 39:04.443
- SO BAUER JUST GETS AWAY
WITH THIS.

39:04.476 --> 39:06.512
- MY BET?
A TAPE LIKE THAT?

39:06.545 --> 39:07.879
SOONER OR LATER IT COMES OUT.

39:07.913 --> 39:09.381
- WELL, WHAT ABOUT
THESE THREE GIRLS?

39:09.415 --> 39:11.517
THEY LIED, UNDER OATH.
THEY JUST GET TO SKATE?

39:11.550 --> 39:14.520
- GENERAL POLICY FOR THE D.A.
IS WHEN YOU GO AFTER GIRLS

39:14.553 --> 39:17.423
WHEN A CASE FALLS APART,
IT CAN PREVENT REAL VICTIMS

39:17.456 --> 39:19.725
FROM COMING FORWARD NEXT TIME.

39:19.758 --> 39:21.560
- I GET THAT.
- YEAH, USUALLY I DO,

39:21.593 --> 39:23.695
BUT THIS TIME?

39:23.729 --> 39:26.097
CARISI, YOU WERE RIGHT ABOUT
THOSE GIRLS ALL ALONG.

39:26.131 --> 39:28.967
- NOT REALLY.
I MISSED BAUER PAID THEM OFF.

39:29.000 --> 39:31.537
- THEY WERE JUST HIS PAWNS.
LIKE SHAKIR, LIKE HIS DAUGHTER.

39:31.570 --> 39:34.540
- I SHOULD HAVE SEEN IT.
JUST RIGHT IN MY BLIND SPOT.

39:34.573 --> 39:37.676
- NO, HE WAS GOOD.
THAT OLD MAN ACT OF HIS?

39:37.709 --> 39:39.711
HE PLAYED US.

39:39.745 --> 39:41.112
WHAT IS THAT EXPRESSION?

39:41.146 --> 39:43.048
"THERE ARE NO
ACCIDENTAL BILLIONAIRES."

39:43.081 --> 39:44.916
[reporters shouting]
- HERE! OVER HERE!

39:46.452 --> 39:48.119
- SHAKIR!
WE HAVE A QUESTION FOR YOU!

39:48.153 --> 39:50.522
COME ON OVER HERE!
SHAKIR!

39:50.556 --> 39:53.124
- I'M, UH...

39:53.158 --> 39:56.562
I'M SO SORRY.
- YEAH.

39:56.595 --> 39:58.196
I LOST MY CONTRACT.
I LOST EVERYTHING.

39:58.229 --> 40:01.567
- YOU HAVE A CASE AGAINST THE
COMPANY, AND MY FATHER, AND--

40:01.600 --> 40:04.470
- I'M NEVER GETTING
MY NAME BACK!

40:04.503 --> 40:07.038
I'M A PUNCH LINE NOW.

40:07.072 --> 40:08.740
YOU GOOGLE ME AND THE FIRST
THING THAT COMES UP

40:08.774 --> 40:11.142
IS "ACCUSED RAPIST."

40:11.176 --> 40:12.778
YOU SHOULD HAVE TRUSTED ME.

40:12.811 --> 40:14.946
- BUT YOU LIED ABOUT
THE OTHER WOMEN.

40:14.980 --> 40:16.948
- I DIDN'T RAPE THEM.

40:24.022 --> 40:26.692
BUT YOU'RE RIGHT.

40:26.725 --> 40:28.627
I'M SORRY.

40:28.660 --> 40:33.131
IT WAS OLD HABIT,
I WAS ON THE ROAD.

40:33.164 --> 40:35.567
IT'S HOW I LOST MY MARRIAGE.

40:41.540 --> 40:45.176
OKAY, I...
I WANT TO BE IN YOUR LIFE.

40:45.210 --> 40:50.949
IF YOU CAN FORGIVE ME,
I'D LIKE TO TRY.

40:50.982 --> 40:54.620
WE CAN START OVER.

40:54.653 --> 40:58.023
A NEW LIFE...

40:58.056 --> 41:00.592
AND WE CAN RAISE
THIS BABY TOGETHER.

41:00.626 --> 41:02.994
- [laughs]

41:10.702 --> 41:15.040
IT'S, UH...
IT'S TOO LATE.

41:15.073 --> 41:17.108
- WHAT DO YOU MEAN?

41:18.710 --> 41:21.947
- THERE IS NO BABY.
NOT ANYMORE.

41:25.784 --> 41:28.486
AFTER TIANA CAME FORWARD,
I, UH...

41:35.260 --> 41:41.266
- [crying]

41:46.137 --> 41:48.540
- ALL THAT HATE
AND THEY'RE STILL TALKING.

41:48.574 --> 41:51.543
- GOTTA BE A TOUGH CONVERSATION.
- I KNOW, RIGHT?

41:51.577 --> 41:53.111
WHERE TO BEGIN?

41:53.144 --> 41:54.846
- ONE OF THEM IS SAYING:

41:54.880 --> 41:58.249
"LET'S START OVER,"
AND THE OTHER ONE IS SAYING...

41:58.283 --> 42:01.286
"IT'S TOO LATE."
